  If you have fonts in your assets and you host your website on Heroku / Amazon S3, you need to do the following steps to make it work.

  - Store all your fonts in the public/fonts folder
  - Create a `public/fonts/all.css` and declare your fonts in it
  - Load your fonts/all.css
    
